sections.text: Terms, defined.For purposes of the Family Home Visitation Act:(1) Department means the Department of Health and Human Services; and(2) Home visitation program means a voluntary program carried out in relevant settings, primarily in the homes of families with one or more children, five years of age or younger, or pregnant persons.SourceLaws 2025, LB22, ยง 2.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
